<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.shaderpredict.MLCompiler</id>
  <name>ML Shader Prediction Compiler</name>
  <summary>AI-powered shader compilation optimization for Steam Deck and Linux gaming</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      ML Shader Prediction Compiler uses machine learning to predict and optimize shader compilation 
      for improved gaming performance on Steam Deck and Linux systems. It features intelligent 
      thermal management, battery awareness, and seamless Steam integration.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI-powered shader compilation prediction and optimization</li>
      <li>Steam Deck hardware optimization with thermal and battery awareness</li>
      <li>P2P shader sharing network for community-driven optimization</li>
      <li>Real-time performance monitoring and adaptive resource management</li>
      <li>Seamless Steam integration with per-game optimization profiles</li>
      <li>Secure sandboxed execution with privacy protection</li>
      <li>Support for Vulkan, OpenGL, and DirectX shaders via translation layers</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Optimized specifically for Steam Deck with automatic detection of LCD vs OLED models,
      gaming mode awareness, and intelligent resource throttling to preserve gaming performance.
    </p>
  </description>
  
